{"tid":691034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支聯會香港中箭琴晚成功 cap 水一百八十萬","createTime":"2018-06-05T10:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T04:27:10.000Z","uid":72280,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"323255134b51d7ed081df0f117722d328ee42c0d","tid":691034,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T10:49:56.000Z","msg":"支聯會昨日舉行六四燭光集會，不少政黨及組織均於場外設街站籌款，其中包括在2016年退出支聯會的專上學生聯會（學聯）。<br />\n<br />\n支聯會及其他泛民政黨亦有在場外進行籌款。支聯會籌得148萬元，香港眾志則籌得33萬元，而社民連及公民黨分別籌得約32萬元及14.5萬元。相比之下，學聯的籌款僅得8,352元，遠遜其他政黨組織。<br />\n<br />\n但有一個夢　cap夠水 種大麻<br />\n無論雨怎麼打　大麻仍是會開花<br />\n但有一個夢　cap夠水　永續吧<br />\n鳩坐就有錢收 永續吧<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/195902/%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B29-%E5%A0%B4%E5%A4%96%E7%B1%8C%E6%AC%BE%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%8A%BD%E6%B0%B4-%E5%AD%B8%E8%81%AF%E5%83%85%E7%B1%8C8%E5%8D%83%E5%A4%9A%E5%85%83-%E9%81%A0%E9%81%9C%E6%94%BF%E9%BB%A8%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F195902%2F%25E5%2585%25AD%25E5%259B%259B29-%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%25B1%258C%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258A%25BD%25E6%25B0%25B4-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2583%2585%25E7%25B1%258C8%25E5%258D%2583%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2585%2583-%25E9%2581%25A0%25E9%2581%259C%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594&d=4nQmkFZQShaVZu8ftzY6XdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=c2f2813f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/195902/%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B29-%E5%A0%B4%E5%A4%96%E7%B1%8C%E6%AC%BE%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%8A%BD%E6%B0%B4-%E5%AD%B8%E8%81%AF%E5%83%85%E7%B1%8C8%E5%8D%83%E5%A4%9A%E5%85%83-%E9%81%A0%E9%81%9C%E6%94%BF%E9%BB%A8%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94</a>"},{"pid":"1141ab08f2c1c23a45f66c195936f754552e7425","tid":691034,"uid":78016,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T10:50:53.000Z","msg":"仲有好多人選擇情花毒<br />\n沒救了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmo